    ⍝ Set: 
    ⍝      Set key value [macro-modes], where macro-modes is either:  
    ⍝      ∘  (1 [isQuote notLiteral]])   
    ⍝      ∘  (0 [rest ignored])        <== DEFAULT...
    ⍝ Note re <value>: Does NOT convert numeric values to string s. Num values used internally...
